Room 1A: Hub (you get your sword and other items) Room that contains items, you get swords, ect. 
Room 1B: First bandit attack on you(All your stuff gets taken), Meeting the horse princess(Beatrice Horseman), she gives you a quest, (Gives health potion)
Room 3:you get another bandit attack
Room 4: Infrimiary: NPC nurse Filipp
Room 5: You meet Boxer and he offers for you to take down the monarchy and start a land ruled equally by all horses. y/n? (continue to Room 8 if no)
Room 6: you get what the horse prince asked for (start going back)

Suggestion:
Princess asks you to bring her the magic sword so she can get rid of all the bandits in the land
Connect the magic fountains with pipes to unlock the room with the magic sword
Boxer asks you for help taking down the princess, says the bandits are a result of poor social services and high taxes forcing people to turn to crime
Bring Boxer to the revolutionary camp and get Boxer's horn, which has an attack description of a bunch of horses charging
Fish at the lake
princess is final fight, team up with boxer for good end

